OL,3,CFormer police officer jailed for
OL,4,Csexual act with woman in patrol car
OL,6,FA former police officer has been
OL,7,Fjailed after the force appealed his
OL,8,Fsuspended sentence for misconduct,
OL,9,Fafter a member of the public performed
OL,10,Fa sex act on him in a patrol car.
OL,12,FMatthew Longmate, 48, formerly of
OL,13,FDerbyshire Constabulary, had been
OL,14,Fgiven a 12-month jail sentence,
OL,15,Fsuspended for a year, after he was
OL,16,Ffound guilty of a single count of
OL,17,Fmisconduct in a public office in
OL,18,FNovember, relating to sexual contact
OL,19,Fwith a woman in his patrol car.
