OL,6,FThe force deemed the sentence unduly
OL,7,Flenient and appealed it, leading the
OL,8,FJudge to remove the suspended sentence
OL,9,Faspect of his conviction.
OL,11,FHe was subsequently jailed for 11
OL,12,Fmonths (12 months minus unpaid work
OL,13,Fserved).
OL,15,FOn 4 October 2015, while on duty, he
OL,16,Fand a colleague offered to take a
OL,17,Fwoman home following an incident at
OL,18,FThe Association bar in Chesterfield.
