OL,6,FThe trial heard that PC Longmate and
OL,7,FPC Daniel Nash parked their car, and
OL,8,Fthe woman had sex with Nash and
OL,9,Fperformed a sex act on Longmate.
OL,11,FLongmate was dismissed from the force
OL,12,Ffollowing his conviction.
OL,14,FDCC Simon Blatchly said "Matthew
OL,15,FLongmate was found guilty of a
OL,16,Fhorrendous crime, where in his role as
OL,17,Fa police officer he not only failed to
OL,18,Fprotect, but actively sought to abuse
OL,19,Fhis position while on patrol.
