OL,6,F"As a force, we felt that a suspended
OL,7,Fsentence did not reflect the severity
OL,8,Fof the offence committed. We therefore
OL,9,Fappealed that decision, and I am
OL,10,Fpleased to see that today he is now in
OL,11,Fcustody.
OL,13,F"The likes of Longmate have no place
OL,14,Fin policing and we will continue to do
OL,15,Fall we can to root out those who taint
OL,16,Fthe hard work of the overwhelming
OL,17,Fmajority of officers and staff in
OL,18,FDerbyshire Constabulary."
